---
description: Rules for parsing, importers, and normalization
globs: src/**/*.rs
alwaysApply: false
---
When working on import and normalization code:
- Keep parser behavior separate from combat math.
- Distinguish clearly between observed log values, inferred values, and assumed values.
- Avoid changing simulator behavior accidentally when editing parsing code.
- Record missing or ambiguous fight state explicitly instead of hiding it.
- Prefer canonical normalized representations before feeding data into simulation.
